iv></div>","info":{"doc":"This evaluates `r := jacobiSym a b` and produces a proof term for the equality.\nThis is done by reducing to `r := jacobiSymNat (a % b) b`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/LegendreSymbol.html#Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.proveJacobiSym","kind":"def","line":332,"name":"Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.proveJacobiSym","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/LegendreSymbol.lean#L332-L351"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/LegendreSymbol.html#Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.proveJacobiSymNat\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">NormNum</span>.<span class=\"name\">proveJacobiSymNat</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ea </span><span class=\"fn\">eb</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Q(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">er</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Q(<a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">ℤ</a>)</span>) × <span class=\"fn\">Q(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/LegendreSymbol.html#Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.jacobiSymNat\">jacobiSymNat</a> <span class=\"fn\">«$ea»</span> <span class=\"fn\">«$eb»</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">«$er»</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This evaluates `r := jacobiSymNat a b` and produces a proof term for the equality\nby removing powers of `2` from `b` and then calling `proveJacobiSymOdd`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/LegendreSymbol.html#Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.proveJacobiSymNat","kind":"def","line":287,"name":"Mathlib.Meta.NormNum.proveJacobiSymNat","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd75